description:
&lt;p&gt;The Patient Safety team at Great Ormond Street Hospital for Children NHS Trust are looking for two (2) dynamic, experienced Patient Safety Managers to join the team. The applicants will have demonstrable experience in Patient Safety, previous experience with Serious Incident Investigations, identifying and sharing learning across the Trust and proactive risk management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Patient Safety Managers will be supporting clinical and non-clinical colleagues with incident review and investigation, monitoring compliance with key work streams and providing teaching/training across the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Patient Safety Team are part of the Quality and Safety team, which are vital for delivering the Quality Priorities of the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details, contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Diane Jones&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Deputy Head of Quality &amp; Safety&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: Diane.Jones@gosh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
